{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4a34f3a8c2","title":"无政府主义是对机会主义的惩罚","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"88ff87694f","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":20,"articleId":"4a34f3a8c2"}],"tags":[{"id":"3be4d5766f","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e2305b9e63","name":"毛泽东","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d263072627","type":"title","text":"无政府主义是对机会主义的惩罚","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4a34f3a8c2"},{"id":"502657f0b5","type":"paragraph","text":"过去的八条，现在的十条结合起来是对的。左派起来了，对立面也起来了，这也不要紧，有点反复有好处。无政府主义是对机会主义的惩罚，要走向反面。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4a34f3a8c2"},{"id":"19c01328a3","type":"paragraph","text":"（现在号召斗、批、改，有人屁股坐不住）毛说：要学生坐得住，要到夏天。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4a34f3a8c2"}],"page":{"id":"4f3b6b8214","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4a34f3a8c2","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}